{"tid":1636145,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"解放軍金鐘「舉槍」戒備 專家料可射強光 令人短暫失明","createTime":"2019-10-07T16:47:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T16:58:11.000Z","uid":68738,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2b8a639b595831e9dc24e6c9c031f7c2392f6c57","tid":1636145,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T16:47:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191007/large/1570450904_0afe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191007%2Flarge%2F1570450904_0afe.png&h=5c2c6d8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n港九多區昨日（6日）爆發大規模示威衝突。解放軍東九龍軍營內有軍人向窩打老道的示威者舉起黃旗示警；網媒《誌》的公民記者亦拍攝到中環軍營有軍人一度「舉槍」戒備。<br />\n<br />\n《誌》主編關震海指，記者昨日下午1時58分拍攝一批示威者在夏慤道架設路障，其間拍到軍營內情況。片段所見，營內3名軍人狀甚緊張，其中一人緊按右腰的疑似槍袋位置，跑到圍牆下戒備；另一軍人亦手持長槍狀武器衝至圍牆下，其間一度向圍牆上方舉槍，未知指向何物，軍營天台亦有多名軍人戒備，視察街外情況。<br />\n<br />\n《誌》曾向中國軍事專家查詢，對方估計軍人所持的長槍狀武器並非實彈槍，有可能是「CS/OW1雷射眩目槍」可發射大功率雷射光線，令目標暫時失明。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191007/60127689?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191007%2F60127689%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=wXQbzQ6sjjdDHWUhljjVf1mNgp3wQ%2BT5fJEe%2BG4C8OY%3D&h=df3dfe63\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191007%2F60127689%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=9eee48c8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191007/60127689?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"d03bdbb941aa0252bb6a63a